# Project Structure

This is a Next.js-based chatbot application that integrates with AI APIs (OpenAI-compatible).

## Main Files

- [app/page.tsx](mdc:lite-llm-chatbot/app/page.tsx) - Main page component with chat interface
- [app/layout.tsx](mdc:lite-llm-chatbot/app/layout.tsx) - Root layout component
- [app/api/chat/route.ts](mdc:lite-llm-chatbot/app/api/chat/route.ts) - API route for chat completion
- [app/config.ts](mdc:lite-llm-chatbot/app/config.ts) - Configuration for API keys

## Project Organization

- `/app` - Main Next.js app directory (App Router)
- `/app/api` - API routes
- `/public` - Static assets
